 <PERSON> George </PERSON> <PERSON> Esper </PERSON> is the <ORGANIZATION> AP </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Northeast </ORGANIZATION> regional reporter, based in <LOCATION> Boston </LOCATION>.
